419
00:50:22,110 --> 00:50:23,510
SPEAKER_03: They shot Long'er?

455
00:53:03,269 --> 00:53:06,710
SPEAKER_03: If you take all our pots away,
how will we cook?

493
00:57:28,099 --> 00:57:29,900
SPEAKER_03: That's a big bowl, Youqing.

494
00:57:29,969 --> 00:57:32,409
SPEAKER_03: Give it to us if you can't finish.

495
00:58:05,139 --> 00:58:07,630
SPEAKER_03: What the hell are you doing?

556
01:03:43,400 --> 01:03:46,199
SPEAKER_03: Youqing, daddy wants you to see the show.

568
01:05:46,059 --> 01:05:49,650
SPEAKER_03: Your boy's on his way with a bowl of tea.

597
01:09:54,750 --> 01:09:56,840
SPEAKER_03: All right. You go on ahead.

670
01:18:33,300 --> 01:18:36,859
SPEAKER_03: Tell him to leave. He killed my son.

671
01:18:36,939 --> 01:18:39,670
SPEAKER_03: - He's already here.
- Tell him to go.

672
01:18:49,890 --> 01:18:51,609
SPEAKER_03: It's me, Chunsheng.

811
01:30:31,350 --> 01:30:33,079
SPEAKER_03: We'd better hurry.

812
01:30:33,149 --> 01:30:35,180
SPEAKER_03: Don't forget your package!

828
01:31:59,470 --> 01:32:01,909
SPEAKER_03: I'll get some water so you can wash up.

899
01:40:16,600 --> 01:40:18,399
SPEAKER_03: Fengxia, you're back!

900
01:40:19,069 --> 01:40:20,340
SPEAKER_03: You cold?

901
01:40:25,909 --> 01:40:27,239
SPEAKER_03: I'm fine, really.

902
01:40:27,319 --> 01:40:29,720
SPEAKER_03: How are you feeling, Mom?

905
01:40:33,989 --> 01:40:35,510
SPEAKER_03: Have you eaten?

915
01:41:33,180 --> 01:41:35,770
SPEAKER_03: Fengxia, you're going to be a mother.

933
01:42:36,880 --> 01:42:38,399
SPEAKER_03: Help yourself.

941
01:43:10,180 --> 01:43:13,109
SPEAKER_03: Fengxia, after the child is born...

942
01:43:13,649 --> 01:43:16,239
SPEAKER_03: have a photo taken every year.

943
01:43:21,489 --> 01:43:24,050
SPEAKER_03: Dad, I saw Chunsheng yesterday.

998
01:47:44,550 --> 01:47:46,539
SPEAKER_03: you still owe us a life!

999
01:47:47,020 --> 01:47:49,079
SPEAKER_03: You've got to value yours!

1000
01:48:14,409 --> 01:48:16,680
SPEAKER_03: Mr. Niu, is your wife at home?

1001
01:48:16,750 --> 01:48:17,810
SPEAKER_03: Yes.

1028
01:49:56,050 --> 01:49:59,180
SPEAKER_03: We'll visit you after
she's out of the hospital.

1034
01:50:21,369 --> 01:50:23,710
SPEAKER_03: Fengxia, don't be nervous.

1035
01:50:23,939 --> 01:50:25,609
SPEAKER_03: Won't hurt a bit.

1036
01:50:26,479 --> 01:50:29,010
SPEAKER_03: Remember to breathe and push.

1037
01:50:29,680 --> 01:50:34,420
SPEAKER_03: When you're pushing, bite on a towel.

1038
01:50:35,659 --> 01:50:37,350
SPEAKER_03: Where's the towel?

1039
01:50:41,760 --> 01:50:46,430
SPEAKER_03: Here, bite on this. It'll save your teeth.

1040
01:50:47,399 --> 01:50:49,829
SPEAKER_03: Do whatever the doctor tells you.

1041
01:50:50,039 --> 01:50:52,130
SPEAKER_03: It'll be quick if you push.

1146
01:59:03,060 --> 01:59:04,260
SPEAKER_03: It's a boy.

1147
01:59:04,329 --> 01:59:07,890
SPEAKER_03: They are fine. He's 7.9 pounds.

1180
02:01:15,329 --> 02:01:16,520
SPEAKER_03: Quick!

